<p class="para">The red dragon darted across it and spewed more flames. Somehow, the black dragon dodged them. Changing its direction towards the gap, the red dragon suddenly soared straight up.</p>
<p class="para">“He’s getting away!” Inuart’s voice shouted from behind them.</p>
<p class="para"><i>‘I won’t fall prey to that black dragon’s claws.’</i></p>
<p class="para">The red dragon stretched out its damaged wings and made way towards the Sky Fortress.</p>
