<p class="para">From the looks of it, however, Furiae seemed uninjured. However, she was horribly pale—her body must have reached its limit… And it was on that frail, paling body that rested the very seal protecting the order of the world.</p>
<p class="para">Caim’s heart filled with both sympathy and love.</p>
