<p class="para">“What are you doing!? Stop giving me those eyes, Caim. Don’t you dare look at me with such contempt…!” Inuart roared. His red eyes shook as if trembling, Caim frowned at him. Strangely, Inuart’s forehead dripped with cold sweat.</p>
